                          <p class="Para">This position statement identifies a&nbsp;number of future applications of multi-agent systems based on information trading economies for large-scale, file-sharing applications. To achieve mass user support, we identify the key requirement for the realisation of such applications as the representation and management of <em class="EmphasisTypeItalic ">individual</em> digital rights. We outline an academic-industrial, Anglo-Japanese research programme fusing a&nbsp;number of base platforms and technologies, whose long-term goal is the development of full-scale applications.</p>
